		  As Lam Research (LRCX) Stock Value Rose, Odey Asset Management Group LTD Has Lowered Position, Crescent Park Management LP Holding in Zoetis (Put) (ZTS) Has Cut by $28.56 Million
		
		
		
		
 

 













































