As Lam Research (LRCX) Stock Value Rose, Odey Asset Management Group LTD Has Lowered Position, Crescent Park Management LP Holding in Zoetis (Put) (ZTS) Has Cut by $28.56 Million


					

						July 25, 2017 - By Clifton Ray

Crescent Park Management Lp decreased its stake in Zoetis Inc (Put) (ZTS) by 71.98% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Crescent Park Management Lp sold 538,900 shares as the company’s stock rose 14.85% with the market. The institutional investor held 209,800 shares of the major pharmaceuticals company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $11.23M, down from 748,700 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Crescent Park Management Lp who had been investing in Zoetis Inc (Put) for a number of months, seems to be less bullish one the $31.13B market cap company. The stock declined 0.47% or $0.3 reaching $62.99 per share. About 1,331 shares traded. Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS) has risen 29.89% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 13.19% the S&P500.







Crispin Odey decreased its stake in Lam Research Corp (LRCX) by 28.13% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Odey Asset Management Group Ltd sold 51,459 shares as the company’s stock rose 32.64% with the market. The hedge fund run by Crispin Odey held 131,501 shares of the industrial machinery and components company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $13.90M, down from 182,960 at the end of the previous reported quarter. Odey Asset Management Group Ltd who had been investing in Lam Research Corp for a number of months, seems to be less bullish one the $26.57 billion market cap company. The stock rose 0.08% or $0.13 reaching $164.25. About 565 shares traded. Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) has risen 107.86% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 91.16% the S&P500.
Analysts await Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) to report earnings on July, 26 after the close. They expect $3.02 earnings per share, up 67.78% or $1.22 from last year’s $1.8 per share. LRCX’s profit will be $488.53M for 13.60 P/E if the $3.02 EPS becomes a reality. After $2.80 actual earnings per share reported by Lam Research Corporation for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts 7.86% EPS growth. 
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.98 in 2016 Q4. Its down 0.20, from 1.18 in 2016Q3. It dived, as 39 investors sold LRCX shares while 225 reduced holdings. 80 funds opened positions while 178 raised stakes. 159.58 million shares or 7.34% less from 172.22 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Checchi Capital Advisers Limited has 0.03% invested in Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX). 77,178 were reported by Retirement Of Alabama. Regions holds 0.02% or 16,183 shares. Caisse De Depot Et Placement Du Quebec holds 43,507 shares. Commonwealth Equity Ser Inc reported 0.01% stake. California-based Assetmark has invested 0.01% in Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX). Barclays Public Ltd Co invested in 0.05% or 396,164 shares. Nuveen Asset Mgmt Ltd Liability holds 325,606 shares. Systematic Fin LP holds 236,022 shares or 0.4% of its portfolio. Bokf Na has invested 0.44% in Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX). Stratos Wealth Ptnrs Limited holds 2,189 shares or 0.01% of its portfolio. Gsa Capital Prns Llp invested 0.09% in Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX). Rgm Cap Limited Co reported 7.81% in Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX). Sun Life Fincl reported 9 shares stake. Westpac accumulated 83,979 shares.
Among 15 analysts covering Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX), 13 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 2 Hold. Therefore 87% are positive. Lam Research Corporation had 41 analyst reports since September 17, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. Citigroup maintained it with “Buy” rating and $102 target in Friday, August 12 report. The rating was maintained by Needham on Thursday, January 26 with “Buy”. On Monday, June 5 the stock rating was maintained by UBS with “Buy”. RBC Capital Markets maintained it with “Underperform” rating and $56.0 target in Thursday, October 22 report. Credit Agricole upgraded Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) on Friday, September 25 to “Buy” rating. Stifel Nicolaus maintained Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) on Monday, November 21 with “Buy” rating. Cowen & Co maintained the shares of LRCX in report on Thursday, December 10 with “Outperform” rating. The firm has “Outperform” rating given on Friday, January 13 by RBC Capital Markets. The stock of Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) earned “Buy” rating by Citigroup on Thursday, October 6. The stock has “Buy” rating by RBC Capital Markets on Monday, June 5.
Since January 31, 2017, it had 0 insider buys, and 20 sales for $38.00 million activity. Anstice Martin B sold $5.80M worth of stock. Shares for $595,150 were sold by ARCHER TIMOTHY on Tuesday, February 28. NEWBERRY STEPHEN G sold $3.01M worth of stock. Bettinger Douglas R had sold 2,556 shares worth $299,103 on Friday, February 10. $759,976 worth of Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) was sold by O’Dowd Sarah A on Monday, March 6. The insider Gottscho Richard A sold 80,009 shares worth $9.96 million.
More notable recent Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) news were published by: Nasdaq.com which released: “Lam Research (LRCX) Q4 Earnings: Is a Beat in the Cards?” on July 24, 2017, also Zacks.com with their article: “Time to Focus on Lam Research (LRCX) for Strong Earnings Growth Potential July …” published on July 12, 2017, Investorplace.com published: “3 Big Stock Charts for Thursday: Tripadvisor Inc (TRIP), Regeneron …” on July 20, 2017. More interesting news about Lam Research Corporation (NASDAQ:LRCX) were released by: Seekingalpha.com and their article: “It’s Time To Pay Attention To Lam Research Corporation” published on July 04, 2017 as well as Benzinga.com‘s news article titled: “Applied Materials, Lam Research: Long Trade Ideas Heading Into Semicon West …” with publication date: July 05, 2017.
Odey Asset Management Group Ltd, which manages about $953.12 million US Long portfolio, upped its stake in Electronic Arts Inc (NASDAQ:EA) by 6,175 shares to 39,025 shares, valued at $3.07 million in 2016Q4, according to the filing. It also increased its holding in Liberty Media Corp Delaware by 65,935 shares in the quarter, for a total of 1.59M shares, and has risen its stake in Discover Finl Svcs (NYSE:DFS). 
Investors sentiment increased to 1.21 in 2016 Q4. Its up 0.02, from 1.19 in 2016Q3. It is positive, as 39 investors sold ZTS shares while 209 reduced holdings. 85 funds opened positions while 215 raised stakes. 450.89 million shares or 0.93% more from 446.74 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Moreover, Ar Asset Management Inc has 0.8% invested in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS). Fieldpoint Private Advsrs holds 14,820 shares or 0.52% of its portfolio. 672,273 are held by First Tru Advsr Limited Partnership. Advantus has 0.07% invested in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS). Zacks Investment accumulated 16,502 shares or 0.03% of the stock. D Scott Neal holds 0% or 119 shares in its portfolio. M&T Financial Bank invested 0.08% in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS). Bessemer Group Incorporated reported 626 shares. Voya Investment Mgmt has invested 0.67% in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS). 82,109 were accumulated by Envestnet Asset Mngmt. Cibc Mkts invested in 0.02% or 88,870 shares. Carroll Inc stated it has 0% in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS). Btc Mgmt reported 35,385 shares. Fayez Sarofim & holds 0.07% of its portfolio in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS) for 246,620 shares. Da Davidson And Co holds 0.17% in Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS) or 137,924 shares.
Another recent and important Zoetis Inc (NYSE:ZTS) news was published by Businesswire.com which published an article titled: “Zoetis to Host Webcast and Conference Call on Second Quarter 2017 Financial …” on June 30, 2017.


